<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/changePassword.css">
		<title>Changer mot de passe</title>
	</head>
	<body>

		<div id="lost_password">
			<h1>Changer votre mot de passe</h1>
			<p>Merci d'indiquer votre nouveau mot de passe.
			<br>Il doit être d'au moins 4 caractères.</p>
			<form action="">
				<div class="input_form">
					<img src="./img/password.png" alt="password">
					<input type="password" placeholder="Mot de passe" name="password">
				</div>
                <div class="input_form">
					<img src="./img/password.png" alt="passwordCheck">
					<input type="password" placeholder="Mot de passe" name="passwordCheck">
				</div>
			</form>
			<button>Valider</button>
			<a id="cancel" href="">Annuler</a>
		</div>

	</body>
</html>
